n"><p>Two death worms swim through the sands.</p></div></div><div class=" slide"><img src="https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/259/87/5.png" alt="A big pile of valuable loot from the roosts and dens of both types of dragons."/><div class="description"><p>A big pile of valuable loot from the roosts and dens of both types of dragons.</p></div></div><div class=" slide"><img src="https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/259/89/7.png" alt="A wild ice dragon explores the area around its roost."/><div class="description"><p>A wild ice dragon explores the area around its roost.</p></div></div><div class=" slide"><img src="https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/286/542/dread_lich.png" alt="a dread lich in a mausoleum along with his summoned minions."/><div class="description"><p>a dread lich in a mausoleum along with his summoned minions.</p></div></div><div class=" slide"><img src="https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/259/95/14.png" alt="two tamed dragons follow their owner in the skies"/><div class="description"><p>two tamed dragons follow their owner in the skies</p></div></div><div class=" slide"><img src="https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/259/84/1.png" alt="A gray fire dragon wanders in the shadow of a glacier."/><div class="description"><p>A gray fire dragon wanders in the shadow of a glacier.</p></div></div><div class=" slide"><img src="https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/264/490/2019-10-01_14.png" alt="A Lectern. This block is used to gather more information about the world Ice and Fire."/><div class="description"><p>A Lectern. This block is used to gather more information about the world Ice and Fire.</p></div></div><div class=" slide"><img src="https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/201/26/hyfgpej.png" alt="A player shows off armor they fashioned from the remains of an ice dragon."/><div class="description"><p>A player shows off armor they fashioned from the remains of an ice dragon.</p></div></div><div class=" slide"><img src="https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/248/785/2019-03-16_14.png" alt="A tamed amphithere sits, while wild ones glide in the background"/><div class="description"><p>A tamed amphithere sits, while wild ones glide in the background</p></div></div><div class=" slide"><img src="https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/227/265/2018-04-07_13.png" alt="Two siren sing a song too beautiful to resist..."/><div class="description"><p>Two siren sing a song too beautiful to resist...</p></div></div><div class=" slide"><img src="https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/311/549/cyclops-cave.png" alt="A cyclops watches over his cave by the sea."/><div class="description"><p>A cyclops watches over his cave by the sea.</p></div></div><div class=" slide"><img src="https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/259/93/12.png" alt="A fire dragon scorches prey off in the distance."/><div class="description"><p>A fire dragon scorches prey off in the distance.</p></div></div><div class=" slide"><img src="https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/227/263/2018-04-07_13.png" alt="Pixie Villages spawn in &quot;Magical Forest&quot; biomes. Pixies will enter and leave their hovels."/><div class="description"><p>Pixie Villages spawn in "Magical Forest" biomes. Pixies will enter and leave their hovels.</p></div></div><div class=" slide"><img src="https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/227/266/2018-04-07_12.png" alt="Two wild hippocampi in the ocean."/><div class="description"><p>Two wild hippocampi in the ocean.</p></div></div><div class=" slide"><img src="https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/259/97/16.png" alt="A roaring flying dragon."/><div class="description"><p>A roaring flying dragon.</p></div></div><div class=" slide"><img src="https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/227/270/2018-04-07_12.png" alt="A sole dragon is attacked by 3 death worms."/><div class="description"><p>A sole dragon is attacked by 3 death worms.</p></div></div><div class=" slide"><img src="https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/259/88/6.png" alt="An ice dragon takes a dive in search of prey."/><div class="description"><p>An ice dragon takes a dive in search of prey.</p></div></div><div class=" slide"><img src="https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/248/786/2019-03-16_15.png" alt="A sea serpent jumps out of the water while chasing a squid."/><div class="description"><p>A sea serpent jumps out of the water while chasing a squid.</p></div></div><div class=" slide"><img src="https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/230/855/2018-06-15_11.png" alt="A troll searches for prey deep underground."/><div class="description"><p>A troll searches for prey deep underground.</p></div></div><div class=" slide"><img src="https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/230/853/2018-06-15_10.png" alt="A cockatrice looks over a savanna."/><div class="description"><p>A cockatrice looks over a savanna.</p></div></div><div class=" slide"><img src="https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/248/787/2019-03-16_15.png" alt="A sea serpent jumps out of the water at sundown."/><div class="description"><p>A sea serpent jumps out of the water at sundown.</p></div></div><div class=" slide"><img src="https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/259/85/3.png" alt="A tamed dragon breathes fire on the command of its owner."/><div class="description"><p>A tamed dragon breathes fire on the command of its owner.</p></div></div><div class=" slide"><img src="https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/259/96/15.png" alt="two dragons glide through the air."/><div class="description"><p>two dragons glide through the air.</p></div></div><div class=" slide"><img src="https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/311/550/lightning-dragon-2.png" alt="An elusive Lightning Dragon raids a Savanna village."/><div class="description"><p>An elusive Lightning Dragon raids a Savanna village.</p></div></div><div class=" slide"><img src="https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/286/543/hydra.png" alt="A hydra with a severed head. It will soon grow back."/><div class="description"><p>A hydra with a severed head. I